Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇见蜗牛的是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:43.35,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(148,585.235)}遇见蜗牛的是我吗
