Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以怎么了 战场原
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问的是 让这家伙
